{{> admin/seatmap/canvas-control/workspace-control}}

<main class="crop-page">
    <aside class="crop-side">
        <section class="crop-panel">
<span class="crop-panel__eyebrow">STEP 01</span>
            <h1>도면 자르기 & 회전</h1>
            <p>원본 PNG를 기준으로 필요한 영역만 정리하고, 버튼 이미지화 단계로 넘깁니다.</p>

            <div class="crop-info">
                <label>현재 도면</label>
                <strong id="cropProjectName">도면 없음</strong>
                <small id="cropProjectPath">새 도면을 먼저 생성하세요.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="crop-actions">
                <button type="button" class="crop-action crop-action--primary" id="applyFullCrop">전체 영역 선택</button>
                <button type="button" class="crop-action" id="openMainPage">메인으로</button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="crop-panel crop-panel--compact">
            <h2>저장 대상</h2>
            <code id="cropSavePath">/temp/seatmap/도면명/seatmap-image.png</code>
        </section>
    </aside>

    <section class="crop-stage">
        <div class="crop-stage__top">
            <strong>미리보기</strong>
            <span>빨간 점선 영역이 저장됩니다.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="crop-canvas-wrap" id="cropCanvasWrap">
            <canvas id="cropCanvas"></canvas>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>